# Project Overview

This project aims to create a link-in-bio platform for Hotels, allowing them to display links, information, and services. Additionally, an AI Concierge will be integrated to assist Hotel customers via a chat interface.

## Key Features
- Dashboard for managing content.
- Public-facing dynamic links for Hotel customers.
- AI Concierge for context-aware assistance.

## Technology Stack
- Next.js with App Directory
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- Shadcn UI and Radix UI components
- Supabase for authentication and database
- AI service for Concierge functionality

## Code Style and Structure
- Concise, technical TypeScript code.
- Functional and declarative programming patterns.
- Modularization over code duplication.
- Descriptive variable names.
- Structured files with exported components, subcomponents, helpers, static content, and types.
